{
  "info": {
    "name": "Event Staffing Platform API",
    "description": "Production-ready two-sided event staffing platform. \n\n## Setup\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Set `base_url` variable to `http://localhost:3000/api/v1`\n3. Run auth flows first to populate tokens\n\n## Test Users (after seeding)\n- SUPER_ADMIN: phone=9999999999\n- ADMIN: phone=8888888888\n- WORKER: phone=7777777777\n\n**OTP appears in server console logs**",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {"key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1"},
    {"key": "admin_token", "value": ""},
    {"key": "user_token", "value": ""},
    {"key": "super_admin_token", "value": ""},
    {"key": "event_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "role_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "application_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "hire_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "chat_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "task_id", "value": ""},
    {"key": "payment_id", "value": ""}
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🏥 Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/../health",
            "description": "Check server is running"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth - Worker",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Send OTP (Worker)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('OTP sent', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));", "console.log('Check server logs for OTP')"]}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/send-otp",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"phone\": \"7777777777\"}"}
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Verify OTP (Worker) → sets user_token",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["const r = pm.response.json();", "if (r.data?.tokens?.accessToken) {", "  pm.collectionVariables.set('user_token', r.data.tokens.accessToken);", "  console.log('Worker token set');", "}"]}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/verify-otp",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"phone\": \"7777777777\", \"otp\": \"REPLACE_WITH_OTP_FROM_LOGS\", \"name\": \"Demo Worker\"}"}
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Set Password (Worker)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/set-password",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"phone\": \"7777777777\", \"password\": \"Demo@123456\", \"confirm_password\": \"Demo@123456\"}"}
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Login (Worker)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"phone\": \"7777777777\", \"password\": \"Demo@123456\"}"}
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/refresh",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"refresh_token\": \"REPLACE_WITH_REFRESH_TOKEN\"}"}
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "6. Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout",
            "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{user_token}}"}]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
